3. I initiated a talk with a gray-area object (I believe) - a dildo. The agent tried to never mention it, but still kept it as indirect object of the call. Upon further asking the agent what object did we initiated the talk with, it couldn't mention it and eventually lost context and couldn't recall what object we had, drifted away. Initiated the same talk with an "orange" instead of a dildo and the agent recalled it perfectly. 

